bio.openEndedText: Hello, I'm Diamond Makena and I like to travel the world, sight see, try out new foods, check out different cultures but most of all, I like to rent nice vehicles when I am away from home. I like to ride around and take a ton of photos of monuments, favourite places, excursions and lots of selfies. I know what it feels like to get to a foreign place and be given the choice of vehicles that's not worth your money; to me, it takes away from the experience. A bad, unreliable, vehicle can ruin an entire trip.. What I wanted to create was a line of luxury vehicles, fully loaded with options, for reasonable rates. This way, travellers using Turo‚Äôs platform for rentals, would have a much better driving experience. I wanted vehicles that would be reliable, full of great features, beautiful inside and out, with working charging ports because travellers need to be able to use their cell phones at all times. Prior to Turo, I was a super host for over five years on airbnb. I had the highest ratings, never had to cancel on a customer. I was always able to provide tips on where to go, places to see, fun excursions, favourite restaurants etc.
